| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1433 — Recovery Inhibition (atomsilo)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 3cba80fc-87b4-5aaf-baef-482d3feec2b4"
